INSERT INTO repair_review (shop_id,rating,comment,author_name,source,is_anonymous,reviewed_at) SELECT shop_id,5,'Highly recommend this shop! First, when I communicated with Hoang the shop owner regarding that I want 20w50 non synthetic oil for my hoopdie old hundred dollar 2006 Yamaha Nuovo, being a foreigner, our communication was challenged! I’ve spoken with other shops and they are annoyed with the communication difficulties. I am very mechanically inclined and understand my bike and particular about how I want it maintained. It’s a cheap old bike. Some things I want done to make it last, others I want to cheap out as the bike isn’t worth the money. Hoang was outstanding about taking the time to understand what I wanted done and we agreed. It was a comfortable process. And then his brother brought us both a free bottle of water while we waited. This is definitely the shop we will take our bike back to for maintenance and repairs. Thanks. Cam on ban! Chúc Mùng Năm Mói!','F Bowles','GOOGLE',false,'2026-02-13 11:40:35.477656+00'::timestamptz FROM repair_shop WHERE external_id='ChIJTT2qzS4vdTERAnQQEzyRHy4';
